                | We&apos;re almost there&comma; building a complete website backed by Nodejs&comma; stored information with MongoDB&comma; and OAuth with Facebook&excl;  We&apos;ve also built an awesome gallery that works like a charm with very minimal code&period;  Now&comma; the last part is simply deploying it so that the website is live and everyone can see it&excl;
