                | &period;  But we&apos;ve actually added a couple new things&comma; so once you&apos;ve finished the tutorial&comma; come back here and we&apos;re going to add the MongoDB capability that we need in order for the gallery to work perfectly&period;
          .row.featurette
            .col-md-3
